headline.main: Paid Notice: Deaths  SIMPSON, ANNE VICKERY

snippet: SIMPSON--Anne Vickery, on March 10, 2016. The Yorkville Community Association deeply mourns the passing of Anne who administered masterfully their charity event for over 40 years. Heartfelt condolences to daughters Marcia Brose and Diane Tompkins. Mrs. Frederick A. Parker, President 1/3
